<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-19-0004 </DOCNO><TEXT>The supply and exploitation of natural gas in Hungary is briefly surveyed.Many data and schemes are given on this subject. Figures are given ofthe past production (1937-1985). Future possibilities of hydrocarbonexploitation are surveyed. General tendencies of the development of thenatural gas industry are mentioned. The role of this industry in Hungarianenergy management is discussed. Finally special problems of the naturalgas industry in Hungary, i.e. technical problems related to the sizeand qualities of the reserves, are examined. 17 figs., 4 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>